videos.headline: Tate sweeps right for Arizona TD
videos.description: Khalil Tate extends Arizona's lead to 14-0 after scoring on a one-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: ASU's Darby hauls in over-the-shoulder catch
videos.description: Frank Darby tracks down a beautiful 48-yard pass and comes down with the catch for Arizona State.

videos.headline: Williams TD catch puts Sun Devils on the board
videos.description: Arizona State cuts the deficit to 14-7 after Kyle Williams finds space in the Arizona's defense and makes the catch to score.

videos.headline: Williams comes down with catch, gets helmet twisted backwards
videos.description: Kyle Williams holds onto a 18-yard catch despite having his helmet twisted all the way around by an Arizona defender.

videos.headline: Ballage bounces over pile for Arizona State TD
videos.description: Kalen Ballage takes the carry and leaps over pile to get into the end zone as the Sun Devils trail the Wildcats 17-14.

videos.headline: Johnson adjusts to make the catch for the Arizona
videos.description: Tyrell Johnson works back to the ball to come down with the 42-yard catch in traffic.

videos.headline: Taylor finds hole in scrambling Arizona State defense for TD
videos.description: Arizona State's defense isn't set when J.J. Taylor gets the carry and runs 15 yards for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Wilkins throws first INT at home this season
videos.description: Lorenzo Burns intercepts Manny Wilkins on an errant throw to give Arizona the ball back with the lead.

videos.headline: Arizona punter drops the snap and gets his punt blocked
videos.description: Jake Glatting drops the long snap and Curtis Hodges breaks through the block the punt with his knee.

videos.headline: Richard breaks through line for Sun Devils' TD
videos.description: Demario Richard lowers his shoulder on the goal-line run to score and cut the deficit to 24-21.

videos.headline: Sun Devils keep momentum with INT
videos.description: Arizona State's Demonte King sits on the corner route and intercepts the pass to give the Sun Devils the ball back.

videos.headline: Wilkins hurdles over defender to give ASU first down
videos.description: On third down in the red zone, Manny Wilkins scrambles and hurdles over the Arizona defender to keep the drive alive.

videos.headline: ASU's Harry reaches out to come down with acrobatic TD catch
videos.description: N'Keal Harry adjusts to snag the touchdown pass in the back corner pf the end zone to give Arizona State the lead.

videos.headline: ASU's Richard runs untouched for long gain
videos.description: Demario Richard finds the hole and rips a 35-yard gain for Arizona State.

videos.headline: Richard extends Sun Devils' lead with second TD
videos.description: Demario Richard bounces the run wide and score from 6 yards out to put the Sun Devils up 35-24.

videos.headline: ASU's Calhoun drags down Dawkins for big sack
videos.description: Arizona's Brandon Dawkins is in at quarterback and loses 15 yards after getting chased down by DJ Calhoun.

videos.headline: Shanked Arizona punt turns into a new set of downs on wacky play
videos.description: Arizona's Josh Pollack drops the snap and shanks the rushed punt, but the short punt hits an Arizona State player, and Arizona recovers to retain possession.

videos.headline: Dawkins fakes reverse and burns Sun Devils for TD
videos.description: Brandon Dawkins fakes the reverse pitch and takes the ball himself 50 yards to the end zone to make it 35-30.

videos.headline: Penalty wipes out miraculous Arizona punt return TD
videos.description: Arizona's Shun Brown reverses field to score on an insane punt return, but the score is called off following a block-in-the-back penalty.

videos.headline: ASU's Harry brings down jump ball for big score
videos.description: N'Keal Harry puts the Sun Devils up two scores after coming down with the jump ball and sneaking a foot in bounds to score a touchdown.

videos.headline: Poindexter elevates for ridiculous grab
videos.description: Arizona's Shawn Poindexter outjumps his defender and hauls in the 48-yard catch.
